{"prompt": "Produce a platform for a mental wellness retreat. The design should be calming, with a mellow yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Serenity Springs Retreat</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #fef3c7; /* Mellow yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #fde68a; /* Slightly lighter yellow */\n            --text-color: #4b5563; /* Dark gray text */\n            --background-color: #fff7e0; /* Very light yellow background */\n            --accent-color: #d97706; /* A warm, subtle accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            min-height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #f59e0b; /* Darker orange on hover */\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-content, .offerings-grid, .testimonials-content {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            text-align: justify;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .offering-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            text-align: center;\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .offering-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .testimonials-content {\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            text-align: center;\n            max-width: 350px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-card p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-card .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .about-content, .offerings-grid {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .about-image {\n                margin-top: 30px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Serenity Springs Retreat</h1>\n        <p>Discover inner peace and rejuvenation at our tranquil sanctuary. Escape the everyday and reconnect with yourself.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Plan Your Escape</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <h2>Embrace Tranquility</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <p>Nestled amidst rolling hills and whispering pines, Serenity Springs Retreat offers a haven for those seeking solace and self-discovery. Our philosophy is rooted in creating a nurturing environment where you can unwind, de-stress, and cultivate a deeper connection with your inner self.</p>\n                <p>We believe that true wellness extends beyond the physical, encompassing mental, emotional, and spiritual harmony. Our programs are designed to guide you on a journey of holistic healing and personal growth.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fef3c7/333?text=Peaceful+Scenery\" alt=\"Serene landscape\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"offerings\">\n        <h2>Our Offerings</h2>\n        <div class=\"offerings-grid\">\n            <div class=\"offering-item\">\n                <h3>Mindful Meditation</h3>\n                <p>Guided sessions to calm the mind and cultivate present moment awareness.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"offering-item\">\n                <h3>Yoga & Movement</h3>\n                <p>Gentle yoga practices to harmonize body and mind, suitable for all levels.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"offering-item\">\n                <h3>Nature Walks</h3>\n                <p>Explore our beautiful surroundings, connecting with nature for therapeutic benefits.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"offering-item\">\n                <h3>Wellness Workshops</h3>\n                <p>Engaging sessions on stress management, self-care, and emotional well-being.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\">\n        <h2>What Our Guests Say</h2>\n        <div class=\"testimonials-content\">\n            <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n                <p>\"Serenity Springs was exactly what I needed. I left feeling refreshed, centered, and with a renewed sense of purpose.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Alex R.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n                <p>\"The peaceful atmosphere and supportive staff made this an unforgettable experience. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Sarah K.</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Ready to Reconnect?</h2>\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n            <p>Contact us today to learn more about our retreat packages and availability.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@serenitysprings.com\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: var(--accent-color);\">Contact Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Serenity Springs Retreat. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}